iled the government's investment strategy as it targets future success at the 2032 Brisbane Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 477, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 358, \"end\": 366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Australian Institute\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 334}, {\"ngram\": \"Sport\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"the government's investment strategy\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"future success\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 441}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2032 Brisbane Olympic Games\", \"from\": 445, \"to\": 476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Albanese government has provided an additional $283 million on top of existing funding for elite sports.\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 483, \"end\": 502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Albanese_government\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 549}, {\"ngram\": \"existing funding\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"elite sports\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 586}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This $283 million in new money, on top of the annual funding that we give, will make a significant difference over the next two years,\\\" Mr Albanese said.\", \"from\": 589, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anthony_Albanese\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Albanese\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \